Evolution
================
 
Evolution is a ruby implementation of a hill-climbing algorithm that uses RMagick to generate a collection of polygons which resemble a baseline image.
 

 
Usage
=====
 
1 - Pick a baseline image you wish to render.
2 - Adjust the path to your baseline image and render directory in the top of evolution.rb
3 - "ruby evolution.rb"

Example: http://joeyschoblaska.com/images/evolution.jpg

 
 
